{"tid":782112,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"想提醒下參加ocamp既動物台手足","createTime":"2018-08-16T12:27:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-22T06:07:28.000Z","uid":8307,"like":97,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"43a5ddf4da3a9f28ae0ea077ce064abcdad6ace1","tid":782112,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T12:27:46.000Z","msg":"一係唔好參加,一係唔好講同動漫有關既野,<br />\n背囊啲公仔都拎走佢,玩驚個陣唔好掛住肝手機驚...<br />\n動漫毒撚會比人杯葛的...<br />\n以前我玩ocamp個陣一開波就圍圈報status<br />\n啲人都正常講下啲拍拖經歷咁樣<br />\n我毒撚又邊有經歷過,咁咪話自己邊個邊個角色我老婆,好多佢既精品同攬枕咁<br />\n佢地聽完即刻淨哂,有啲好人啲既都話自己有睇下刀劍咁<br />\n之後個組爸話我有冇同條女一齊影既相...<br />\n我答唔出，之後成程都冇出過聲<br />\n成個大學生涯都冇人加過我入谷..."},{"pid":"92e682e6d48c777d26020321c5c6833e7fd435ed","tid":782112,"uid":34293,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T12:30:06.000Z","msg":"愛回家幾好睇"},{"pid":"0f9a5be6856151b415b7634a8f44fabc8646f919","tid":782112,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"92e682e6d48c777d26020321c5c6833e7fd435ed","tid":782112,"uid":34293,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T12:30:06.000Z","msg":"愛回家幾好睇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T12:31:38.000Z","msg":"翻睇多次大老師好過"},{"pid":"15c2309adca65462a3dc194bc007b18e40e8cbe7","tid":782112,"uid":62837,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T12:33:18.000Z","msg":"D動漫研究會 d人好撚恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c84f81df249e61f3f704a9b55e75395cbbf194a4","tid":782112,"uid":35667,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T12:33:54.000Z","msg":"刀劍不錯"},{"pid":"9ddf3b070f2c73d07a457f29a283c342ddab3a3d","tid":782112,"uid":8307,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"15c2309adca65462a3dc194bc007b18e40e8cbe7","tid":782112,"uid":62837,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T12:33:18.000Z","msg":"D動漫研究會 d人好撚恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T12:39:16.000Z